    body: `Chiki the squirrel had a little pile of nuts. Snow began to fall — brrr! A tiny bird shivered nearby, hungry and cold. "Here, share my nuts," said Chiki. She gave the bird a plump one to nibble. "Cheep, thank you!" Together they snuggled in the cozy tree-hollow, warm and full, while the soft snow fell outside.`,
